The paper deals with image processing problems and the evaluation of segmentation algorithms, which are typically studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of ground truth and annotator agreement is also relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) research.
